title: Best_Digital_and_Film_Photography_Books
description:
This torrent includes (for private personal use):

* Closeups In Nature. The photographer&#039;s guide to techniques in the field (John Shaw, 1987).djvu
* John Shaw&#039;s Nature Photography Field Guide 2000 version.pdf
* Learning_to_See_Creatively__Revised_Edition__Bryan_Peterson.pdf
* Mastering_Digital_Printing__2nd_ed__Harald_Johnson.pdf
* Real_World_Adobe_Photoshop_CS2__Bruce_Fraser__David_Blatner.chm
* The Adobe Lightroom Ebook For Digital Photography (Scott Kelby, 2006).pdf
* The_Digital_Photography_Book__Scott_Kelby.chm
* The_Photoshop_CS2_Book_for_Digital_Photographers__Scott_Kelby.chm
* Understanding_Exposure__Revised_Edition__Bryan_Peterson.pdf

If you enjoy them, you should consider supporting the authors by buying them.



I would like to get:

* The Camera, The Negative and The Print by Ansel Adams
* Photography by Barbara London and John Upton
* Understanding Shutter Speed by Bryan Peterson
* The A-Z of Creative Digital Photography by Lee Frost
* Complete Digital Photography by Ben Long
* John Hedgecoe?s Complete Guide to Photography by John Hedgecoe
* The Photographer?s Guide to Filters also by Lee Frost
* Beyond Portraiture: Creative People Photography by Bryan Peterson
* Mountain Light: In Search of the Dynamic Landscape by Galen A. Rowell
* Spirit of Place: The Art of the Travelling Photographer by Bob Krist
* The Basic Book of Photography by Tom and Michelle Grimm
* The Art of Outdoor Photography by Boyd Norton

If you happen to have any of them, please share it and announce your torrent in a comment.


Happy shooting!
